{"tid":936044,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)熱爆MADAM 選美俏臥底1-2 凸務MADAM","createTime":"2018-12-10T13:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T19:36:43.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32474bfb528036446d9631804d20b188335dfb9a","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=173eb445\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8101f9dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ec3ae241\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Heat_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Heat_poster.jpg&h=d675e178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d4/MissCongeniality_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd4%2FMissCongeniality_poster.jpg&h=4e11cf4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5d/Spy2015_TeaserPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5d%2FSpy2015_TeaserPoster.jpg&h=8e121664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.精明細心的聯邦調查局女探員Sarah Ashburn接受上級委派的任務，到波士頓去抓捕大毒梟Simon Larkin，到之後與當地警察局一位辦事粗魯的女警員Shannon Mullins展開合作對付毒販，她倆在辦案過程中搞出了不少笑話<br />\n<br />\n2.葛蕾絲&middot;哈特（珊卓&middot;布拉克飾演）是一位表現出色、富正義感的聯邦調查局探員，由於她的外表不吸引人，加上她剛正不阿的性格，讓局裡面的男性同事都把她當哥兒們看待，不過和葛蕾絲共事多年的拍檔艾瑞克&middot;馬修斯（班傑明&middot;布拉特飾演）卻不這麼想，他認為葛蕾絲其實也有溫柔的一面，只是還沒被挖掘出來。<br />\n這天，美國境內的最大犯罪集團「公民」發出黑函，揚言將在美國小姐選美會場上放置炸彈，屆時不只美國小姐的生命受到威脅，現場觀禮的嘉賓可能也難逃池魚之殃<br />\n<br />\n3.在這部續集中珊卓布拉克飾演的FBI幹員桂西哈特因為在美國小姐選美大會中臥底，並成功解除一起恐怖攻擊事件之後，在一夜之間成為媒體寵兒。但是最近她的狀況又不佳，因為她才剛跟男友分手，現在又發現她成天都被狗仔隊偷拍，害她無法從事她最喜歡的臥底行動，所以她覺得自己這個英雌變得無用武之地。但是她在聯邦調查局的上司可不這麼想，他們認為以她目前的知名度，最適合上遍電視上的大小節目<br />\n<br />\n4.一名美國中央情報局（CIA）內勤數據分析師蘇珊&middot;庫柏（梅莉莎&middot;麥卡錫飾），長期協助著外勤探員布萊德利&middot;范恩（裘德&middot;洛飾）。胖胖的蘇珊，是個傑出的數據分析專家，也是范恩的左右手，長期合作之下，對俊俏的范恩有著若有似無的情愫。但范恩與美女軍火商蕾娜&middot;波楊諾（蘿絲&middot;拜恩飾）交鋒時卻出師不利，讓CIA喪失了一員猛將，惡毒的蕾娜&middot;波楊諾居然還列出CIA的精銳特工名單<br />\n<br />\n9 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f2eff949\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=vhMmb7iG28eVNpKDmNqN3p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=44d683f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f7454bcb50624650bebfbd3503a1491ebc3ec9","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900e91414f942c2269110fb4918d8a8e3b54d721","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666bc11542cfaf6a08eb9b2c0b94aca455333d71","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fd669b3143f86f630e03fd7a51259f265964f2","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710c92d5f863d02a23807afeda1a943aa453fbf8","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f443ecd5f2903a61abf15449677afe89f0962f","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc090ed3567b83db6e09f63bc4d55b5ddd6e7b22","tid":936044,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s